    PERSONAL TRAINING

    Hey, you! I'm Ashley

     Your Personal Coach, Here To Make A Positive Impact.

    As a professional trainer, my passion is to guide the world towards a healthier lifestyle. Everybody is unique, with their own strengths and limitations. My method is to build a custom plan based on your health, schedule and more importantly, fitness goals. I aim is to have your mind and body work in harmony, to transform your body and influence you to make more mindful decisions when it comes to your health.

    Working in an Activ Balance fitness program is like no other experience. I'm here to work on both your body and your mind in partnership. It’s hard work, but it’s the right work – and that’s why it pays dividends. I'm here to actively help you achieve the balance you've always wanted when it comes to fitness, health, and your normal day-to-day. Whether you're a high-flying professional, a mother juggling it all, or someone who is looking for a method that works for you specifically, you're at the right place. There are no tricks! Instead, the only ingredients are determination, desire, knowledge, and consistency.

    You will work well with me if; 

    • You're prepared to put in the hard graft. 

    • You're looking to find a healthy balance in your life.

    • You're looking to train virtually, online, or in-person.

    • You'll trust the process and not compare yourself to others.

    • You're looking for guidance in and outside of your workouts. 

    • You're excited to get yourself into an incredible space in both mind and body.

    • You're prepared to develop new habits that will ultimately lead you to a new lifestyle.

    THE ULTIMATE METHOD TO CHANGING YOUR LIFE

    Introducing the Six Pillars of Health and Wellbeing method.

    Activ Balance is here to help you stay fit and healthy beyond your sessions. Throughout your time with your coach, you will be able to expand your knowledge and skills in the following six pillars ;

    Staying Active (Including breathwork)

    Hydration

    Nutrition (Wholefood Eating)

    Mobility & Stretching

    Sleep

    Mindset

    These are aspects of your life that are key to truly improving your lifestyle or to aid in maintaining your current healthy lifestyle. I will ensure you feel supported all the way with a program tailored to your needs and accountability checks at a time that suits you. Everyone has their own journey and everyone started from somewhere. 

    With an Activ Balance program, expect;

    A tailored program to suit your plan or goal

    Weekly check-ins

    Accountability in a format that works for you

    Guidance in lifestyle and/or nutrition

    Workout sessions that promote functional, creative movement.

    PERSONAL TRAINING

    The Time Is Now!

    There can be a million excuses you tell yourself why you aren't "ready" for Personal Training...

    You know you want to make the change, however you have been stuck in a loop that leaves you feeling overwhelmed and confused. By the time you are ready to begin, you are in a much different body to what you last recognised. I fully understand this cycle you're in. I've been there. 

    At the beginning of most of my client's journey, I literally have the most wonderful, highly intelligent and beautiful people apologise to me for their first in-take photo that they send me. The level of self-esteem is universally super low. I'm here to take that level and elevate it to a place you weren't expecting. I have clients that now frequently adorn swimsuits out on the beach, influence their children to strive to be healthier, take part in races and competitions of the first time and more. When they began their sessions with me, they were only focussing on "toning up" or "dropping a dress size" - what they didn't expect was learning to genuinely love themselves when they look back in the mirror or take new life challenges in their life. 

    Your abilities are endless. The first step is acknowledging you want the accountability and the guesswork to be taken away. The second step is turning up, the third turning up, the fourth....well you guessed it. It's time to dedicate time in your week to you and to you only. Say goodbye to your other hats when you enter your session. No more mum, dad, wife, brother, boss, employee, business owner, carer. You turn up to your workout as YOU. 

    What are you waiting for?! Come and join the dozens of other Activ Balance clients and achieve, health, happiness and a far stronger version of yourself. 

    Personal Training

    So you've made the big decision to get your life in order. You know what to do, you've decided where is best for you to train, you know ideally know what are the best things to eat. But then you have an overwhelming sense of no idea how many times to train, how much or how little to eat, what type of movement is best for you and then you're back at square one. Don't worry, Activ Balance has got you covered. Whether you'd like to train online through live video calls, virtually through an online program, or even in person (at your home or the gym), it's possible for you to begin your journey! Enjoying your sessions is extremely important and you are embarking on a journey where you trust the process. Come in and join dozens of other Activ Balance clients and truly fall in love with your future self.

    Small Group Personal Training

    If like me, you're more of a wolf-pack than a lone wolf personality, Small Group PT is the perfect approach to your fitness goals. Your program is specifically designed around the Coach Harrogate gym, where you will be able to sweat it out in; the boxing room, the spin room, the main gym floor, the main classroom and the Evolution room! Expand your knowledge no matter where you have started. Feel yourself getting stronger each week through our weekly challenges. Support and be supported by your SGPT peers in your very own private Whatsapp group chat. Sessions are a monthly subscription of only £11.25 per week!

    Fitness Classes

    Want to burn over 500 calories in a creative fitness class?  Or possibly you're looking to expand and practise your mindfulness with a deep Savasana class. Quite possibly you also want to improve your mobility, join in our workshop-based fascia release and deep stretch class.  With over 15 classes on offer per week, there is so much to choose from; from Core Conditioning, Functional Training, Stretch, Hiit, Body Condition and Wellbeing. Over 600 classes have been taught in Harrogate in the past year, with thousands of attendees, most returnees. Curious about it? Come and join us at Nuffield and/or Coach in Harrogate.
